ÄúExtra Charge‚Äù items title. Setting Extra Charges New [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Bernat Torras\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3174:\"<h2>WooCommerce Pay for Payment</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-pay-for-payment/\">http://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-pay-for-payment/</a></p>\n<h2>Extension Description</h2>\n<p>Add individual charges for each payment method as a flat rate and/or as a percentage of the cart total. The plug-in first calculates the percentage rate and then adds the fixed rate on top.</p>\n<h2>Fixed Issues</h2>\n<p>Ability to translate the ‚ÄúExtra Charge‚Äù items title.</p>\n<h2>Setting Extra Charges</h2>\n<p>New fields were added on each ‚ÄúPayment method‚Äù configuration page. These fields allow the user to add an extra charge that will be applied when the customer selects a payment method. It is also possible to customize the label that will appear for this extra charge.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_435741\" style=\"width: 258px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/backend.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-435741 size-medium\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/backend-248x300.png\" alt=\"Setting Extra Charges\" width=\"248\" height=\"300\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Setting Extra Charges</p></div>\n<h2>Translating Extra Charges</h2>\n<p>The extra charges titles can be translated directly in WPML&gt;Strings Translation.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_435744\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/st-2.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-435744 size-medium\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/st-2-300x172.png\" alt=\"Translating Extra Charges\" width=\"300\" height=\"172\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Translating Extra Charges</p></div>\n<h2>Frontend</h2>\n<p>When a customer selects an extra-charged payment method, a new row will appear displaying the extra charge title with the extra amount. This field appears translated in secondary languages, and the price is also filtered using the current currency.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_435748\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/checkout.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-435748 size-medium\" src=\"http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/checkout-300x296.png\" alt=\"Translated Strings in Checkout page\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Translated Strings in Checkout page</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=ES2sf1kOD2s:c0xZAXl2sQ8:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=ES2sf1kOD2s:c0xZAXl2sQ8:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=ES2sf1kOD2s:c0xZAXl2sQ8:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=ES2sf1kOD2s:c0xZAXl2sQ8:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=ES2sf1kOD2s:c0xZAXl2sQ8:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=ES2sf1kOD2s:c0xZAXl2sQ8:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/ES2sf1kOD2s\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\